  "description": "Villa Los Naranjos is a large and spacious traditional-styled villa with a beautiful pool and garden and impressive open views over the Los Naranjos Golf Course.\n\nThis charming villa offers 4 double ensuite bedrooms and various entertainment and dining areas, providing a comfortable and impressive space to enjoy your holidays in one of the best locations in Marbella.\n\nThe entrance hall leads to the living room and dining area with access to the outside terrace. These bright and airy rooms have great views. The lounge features a fireplace for the cooler evenings, ceiling fans for the summer and a Television with UK channels.\n\nThe large country-styled kitchen can be accessed from the hallway or the dining room; There is an American fridge/freezer, an ice-maker, and various other small appliances. There is a breakfast table in the kitchen and large double doors that open to the covered patio that has an outdoor lounge area and a built-in BBQ. This is a wonderful area to dine, at any time of day, with the sprawling views of the Golf Course.\n\nThe Villa features fabulous outdoor entertainment areas: 2 lounge areas with comfortable seating, one dining area with a gas BBQ, a swimming pool with slide (and option to heat) and a lovely level grassed garden, all enjoying the stunning open views.\n\nOn the entrance level there is a double bedroom with a full ensuite bathroom and direct access to the garden and terraces. There is also a guest bathroom off the hallway.\n\nUpstairs are three double bedrooms all ensuite with bathtubs and each with their own terrace, overlooking the Golf Course with very relaxing open views. Two bedrooms have double beds and one has twin singles.\n\nThere is space to park 3 cars behind the electric gates (parked one behind the other).\n\nThe Villa has central heating throughout, AC in the bedrooms and ceiling fans in the living room. There is an interior alarm and wifi.\n\nVilla Los Naranjos is in the heart of the Marbella’s Golf Valley, very close to all amenities and just a few minutes down to the beach and Puerto Banús. Also, the many restaurants, bars and nightlife of Nueva Andalucia are easily reached in a few minutes’ drive.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you.",
